493
00:26:49,380 --> 00:26:50,290
Sa tingin ko

494
00:26:50,490 --> 00:26:52,550
Tapos ka na talaga sa karera.

495
00:26:55,690 --> 00:26:57,220
Salamat sa iyong katapatan.

496
00:26:58,720 --> 00:26:59,680
Kaya,

497
00:27:00,450 --> 00:27:02,250
