558
00:30:43,490 --> 00:30:44,140
Sanlai

559
00:30:44,680 --> 00:30:45,480
at ang Baliw na Jin.

560
00:30:45,820 --> 00:30:46,620
Sino pa?

561
00:30:50,580 --> 00:30:52,210
Sabihin mo sa akin ang totoo.

562
00:30:56,290 --> 00:30:57,450
Ginawa ba ni Sanlai

563
00:30:58,380 --> 00:30:59,580
