573
00:31:26,450 --> 00:31:27,050
Hindi.

574
00:31:27,660 --> 00:31:28,340
Tingnan mo.

575
00:31:28,690 --> 00:31:29,900
Hindi mo agad itinanggi.

576
00:31:29,900 --> 00:31:30,820
Nag-alangan ka.

577
00:31:31,130 --> 00:31:33,930
Hindi mo ako sinasagot.
Hindi ka tapat.

578
00:31:41,300 --> 00:31:42,410
Gising na ako.

579
00:31:45,920 --> 00:31:46,640
Nasaan siya?

580
00:31:56,530 --> 00:31:57,730
Saan siya pumunta?

581
00:32:02,970 --> 00:32:08,730
[Bumili kami ng almusal. Hintayin mo ako.]

582
