597
00:33:29,180 --> 00:33:30,910
Ayaw ni Mu ng berdeng sili.

598
00:33:33,470 --> 00:33:34,350
Ginang, pakitimbang po ang mga ito.

599
00:33:34,350 --> 00:33:34,980
Dito.

600
00:33:37,630 --> 00:33:38,990
-Tadyang baboy.
-2.80 yuan.

601
00:33:39,230 --> 00:33:40,360
Bumibili ka pa?

602
00:33:41,090 --> 00:33:42,490
Binata, 2.80.

603
00:33:44,340 --> 00:33:45,060
Sige.

604
00:33:45,830 --> 00:33:47,200
Ginoo, pakitimbang po ang mga tadyang na ito.

605
00:33:47,200 --> 00:33:48,050
Sigurado.

606
00:33:49,350 --> 00:33:50,350
Sariwa ba ang karne?

607
00:33:50,440 --> 00:33:51,400
Napakapresko.

608
00:33:52,970 --> 00:33:54,430
Gaano pa kaya tayo katagal?

609
00:33:54,490 --> 00:33:55,050
Halos tapos na.

610
00:33:55,050 --> 00:33:57,210
Hindi ba ikaw ang
gustong sumama?

611
00:33:57,210 --> 00:33:59,210
Pero hindi ko inaasahan ang ganitong sitwasyon.

612
00:33:59,270 --> 00:34:00,930
Sandali lang. Isa na naman.

613
00:34:02,920 --> 00:34:03,710
Mga itlog sa bukid.

614
00:34:03,990 --> 00:34:04,580
Mga itlog sa bukid?

615
00:34:04,580 --> 00:34:06,710
-Ginoo, hindi pa po kayo nagbabayad!
-Ano po iyon?

616
00:34:07,100 --> 00:34:07,770
Magbayad.

617
00:34:08,560 --> 00:34:09,780
Magbayad doon gamit ang QR code.

618
00:34:09,780 --> 00:34:10,650
Sige.

619
00:34:30,250 --> 00:34:30,810
Timbangin ang mga ito.

620
00:34:30,810 --> 00:34:31,440
Sige.

621
00:34:35,860 --> 00:34:36,790
Patatas, itlog.

622
00:34:37,610 --> 00:34:38,219
Nakuha ko na sila.

623
00:34:38,370 --> 00:34:39,179
Mga tadyang.

624
00:34:39,830 --> 00:34:40,460
Nakuha ko.

625
00:34:40,739 --> 00:34:42,739
Repolyo, talong, kulantro.

626
00:34:42,900 --> 00:34:43,699
Nakuha ko na sila.

627
00:34:44,340 --> 00:34:45,610
Edamame, pipino.

628
00:34:46,130 --> 00:34:47,090
Nakuha ko na sila.

629
00:34:47,449 --> 00:34:50,820
Mga berdeng sibuyas, litsugas, dalandan, saging.

630
00:34:50,820 --> 00:34:51,570
Nakuha mo na ang lahat?

631
00:34:51,570 --> 00:34:52,420
Oo.

632
00:34:57,970 --> 00:34:59,300
Ano ba 'yang nginingiti-ngiti mo?

633
00:35:01,220 --> 00:35:02,550
Kakaiba ang kinikilos mo.

634
00:35:04,480 --> 00:35:05,790
Paano ba ako kumikilos nang kakaiba?

635
00:35:05,790 --> 00:35:07,190
Hindi ka nagpaplano

636
00:35:07,790 --> 00:35:08,980
Magpakasal ka kay Mu, 'di ba?

637
00:35:13,410 --> 00:35:15,100
