641
00:35:18,890 --> 00:35:20,220
-Ano ang hitsura nito?
-Kailangan ko talaga ng tulong para mahanap ito.

642
00:35:20,220 --> 00:35:21,770
Ito'y... Ganito kalaki.

643
00:35:21,770 --> 00:35:23,900
-May apat na karakter na Tsino dito.
-Ah, sige.

644
00:35:23,900 --> 00:35:24,740
Pakiusap, kailangan mo akong tulungan.

645
00:35:24,740 --> 00:35:27,130
-Napakahalaga talaga.
-Sige, naiintindihan ko.

646
00:35:27,170 --> 00:35:28,090
Nagmamakaawa ako sa iyo.

647
00:35:28,090 --> 00:35:28,780
Hanapin mo naman.

648
00:35:28,780 --> 00:35:31,260
Nawalan ng gamit ang isang pasahero.

649
00:35:31,260 --> 00:35:32,780
Isa itong keychain

650
00:35:33,090 --> 00:35:35,260
