651
00:35:47,080 --> 00:35:47,850
Pasensya na.

652
00:35:49,580 --> 00:35:50,630
Opo, ​​ginoo.

653
00:35:52,900 --> 00:35:54,260
May nakita akong keychain.

654
00:35:54,330 --> 00:35:55,960
Pag-aari 'yan ng babaeng 'yan.

655
00:35:56,390 --> 00:35:58,120
Maaari mo bang ibigay ito sa kanya?

656
00:35:58,410 --> 00:35:59,510
-May apat na salitang Tsino dito.
-Sige.

657
00:35:59,510 --> 00:36:00,110
Salamat.

658
00:36:00,340 --> 00:36:01,540
Gawa ito sa katad.

659
00:36:01,610 --> 00:36:03,090
Nakasulat doon ang "Zhao at Mu".

660
