662
00:36:06,120 --> 00:36:06,850
Kumusta.

663
00:36:08,490 --> 00:36:09,290
Ito ba ang isang ito?

664
00:36:11,700 --> 00:36:12,780
Oo, iyon lang.

665
00:36:13,860 --> 00:36:14,570
Salamat.

666
00:36:14,600 --> 00:36:15,290
Walang anuman.

667
00:36:15,290 --> 00:36:15,960
